Opens DMVA for the specified grammar model.

Closes DMVA. Closes DMVA and frees up resources. Aborts all active dialogs and removes any transactions that were scheduled. DMVA will continue the closing process asynchronously and will transition to the Closed state when it has finished closing. If DMVA is already in the Closing state, the request won't be processed and NUSAVirtualAssistantErrorCodeApplicationStateError is returned. Once close is called, you'll need to call open again to use DMVA.
